================================================================================
CURRENT APPLICATION STATE
================================================================================

The application is fully functional and running at: http://localhost:5174/

Users can:
1. View dashboard with metrics
2. Click "Sync Catalogs" to load available catalogs
3. Select a catalog from the dropdown
4. View schemas in Column 2
5. Click a schema to load tables in Column 3
6. Use schema dropdown to switch between schemas
7. Navigate using browser back/forward buttons
8. View all metadata in a clean, modern interface

================================================================================
NEXT DEVELOPMENT PHASE
================================================================================

The foundation is complete. Ready to build:

1. COLUMN EXPLORER
   - Display column metadata (name, type, nullable, comment, position)
   - Show when table is selected

2. SENSITIVE DATA DETECTION
   - Rule-based PII detection (email, phone, Aadhaar, PAN, passport, etc.)
   - Visual indicators for sensitive columns

3. CLASSIFICATION SYSTEM
   - Public / Internal / Confidential / Restricted
   - Colored badges for each classification

4. PRIVACY POLICIES
   - Masking policies (email, PAN, Aadhaar, salary)
   - Hide policies
   - Role-based access
   - Country restrictions
   - Retention policies

5. POLICY ASSIGNMENT
   - Assign policies to catalog/schema/table/column
   - Policy management interface

6. COMPLIANCE DASHBOARDS
   - GDPR compliance
   - HIPAA compliance
   - PCI DSS compliance
   - SOC2 compliance
   - ISO27001 compliance
   - Compliance scores and policy coverage

7. AUDIT LOGS
   - Track policy creation
